> type of eating experience. If you haven't tried it...now's your chance!

> Our take is weeknight-friendly (i.e. doesn't take hours) and features a bounty
> of tender shrimp. On the side, there's warm garlicky ciabatta for sopping
> up every last drop of that broth, and a green salad with pickled apple and
> crispy Parmesan frico. Once bite and you'll be hooked (line and sinker).